  project. For the external link functionality, the agent first implemented a
  solution within the renderer process to intercept  events. When
  this proved insufficient for all cases, particularly popups, the agent pivoted
  to a more robust approach in the main process, utilizing
   to ensure all external links are opened
  correctly. The agent also managed the build process, addressing minor issues,
  and deployed the updated application to the user's Applications folder.
